channel.description:
NEVER TRY MS Paint in your entire life! It takes freaking hours just to make a god dang coin! LOL I swear! Took me 3 straight hours just to get the screen right. and about 1 hour to fix the keyboard because I had it spaced out to far so I have to shorten it.
Ma coin XD: [IMG]http://i12.tinypic.com/4unbpxl.jpg[/img] very first image in MS Paint and the below dark part is suppose to be shadow if you wondering.
Ma lil logo I was working on: [IMG]http://i18.tinypic.com/67ehfra.jpg[/img] I made this for a thread I had a post reserved on.
